Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.82,0:22:11.42,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\blur3}The words will make you out 'n' out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:16.75,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\blur3}I spend the day your way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:24.01,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\blur3}Call it morning driving thru the sound and in and out the valley
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:34.59,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\blur3}The music dance and sing
